data.description: PERFECT for Your Personal Touches, this charming 4-Level Home has Timeless Appeal! With a little TLC this perfectly situated home offers a prime location with easy access to the golf course. Nestled amidst Mature Trees, this Home Boasts a Serene Atmosphere and Plenty of Outdoor Space to Enjoy. Step onto the Large Deck, ideal for Entertaining or Unwinding after a Long Day. Recently Refreshed fencing and exterior this home just need a little brush up to shine. A handy person with the right tools will be able to make this house a home in no time! Step Inside to Discover a Spacious Sunroom, Providing a Tranquil Retreat bathed in Natural Light. The Family Room, Complete with a Cozy Fireplace, Invites Gatherings and Relaxation. Both Formal and Informal Dining Spaces Offer Versatility for Any Occasion. This home has been well-loved and is just waiting for your personal touches to make it dazzle. There is a roughed in gas line for the dryer as you update towards greener utilities and a generous enclosed patio with natural lighting and cooling for those hot summer days when you long for the outdoors without the heat. There is ample space for living and entertaining. The esthetics of the home were meticulously taken into consideration and this home is priced accordingly. This home will serve new owners well and is just waiting for your updates and special touches. Enclosed porch is NOT included in square footage and adds approximately 300 soft more living space. Don't forget about the garage with a Sturdy Workbench and shelving for all of your home projects. Buyer or Buyer's agent to verify all square footage measurements. Motivated and priced to MOVE!!! All offers will be presented, please allow 48 hours acceptance deadline. All REASONABLE offers considered.This diamond in the rough won't last long!! Please allow 2 hours notice before showing. OPEN HOUSE scheduled for 4/27 - 10am-2pm, bring your buyers and investors!! 48 hour acceptance deadline on all offers.
